picograd: torch.Tensor->{PTX, Triton} compiler
disclaimer: this is a one man effort to compile llama2. beware of dragons.
versions:
- 0.1.1: hackable. llama2able.
- 0.1.2: multi-node. multi-gpu.
- 0.1.3: multi-datacenter.
references:
  - hardt/recht, jurafsky/martin, scardapane, murphy, goodfellow/bengio, prince
  - hwu et al, cheng et al, hennesey/patterson